data.meta_description: Victor Amadeus ii van Savoye was born on May 14, 1666, son of Charles Emanuel ii van Savoye and Marie Jeanne van Savoye. He was married on April 10, 1684 to Anne Marie van Orleans, they had 3 children. He died on October 31, 1732. This information is part of Genealogy John Muijsers by John Muijsers on Genealogy Online.
